article.description: — Vladimir Pinchuk had 15 points off the bench to lead San Diego to a 103-38 win over La Verne Tuesday night.
article.headline: San Diego crushes La Verne 103-38 in season opener
article.linkText: San Diego crushes La Verne 103-38 in season opener
article.story: SAN DIEGO -- — Vladimir Pinchuk had 15 points off the bench to lead San Diego to a 103-38 win over La Verne Tuesday night. Terrell Brown had 13 points and three blocks for San Diego. Jase Townsend added 13 points. Yavuz Gultekin had 12 points and 11 rebounds. Paul Antonis had 10 points and eight rebounds for the Leopards. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
